  <div class="intro">
    <span>Hi, I'm Eder Rengifo.<br><a href="https://dribbble.com/ederrengifo" target="_blank">Designer</a>, amateur <a href="https://github.com/ederrengifo" target="_blank">coder</a>, <a href="https://medium.com/@ederrengifo" target="_blank">writer</a> <br>and I also like to make <a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/14hnNArAo2xat2a89Uyoze" target="_blank">music.</a></span>
